1982;;Next of Kin;;Australian;;Tony Williams;;Jacki Kern, John Jarratt, Alex Scott, Gerda Nicolson, Charles McCallum, Bernadette Gibson, Robert Ratti, Tommy Dysart;;horror;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Next_of_Kin_(1982_film);;Linda (Kerin) inherits a retirement home called Montclare, a foreboding but apparently harmless place. While on a trip home to settle her deceased mother's estate, strange deaths begin to occur in the home.